[
    {
        "text": "Email is one of those potentially powerful tools that actually turns into an Achilles' heel if not managed.",
        "startTime": 81,
        "endTime": 6679,
        "slowStartTime": 272,
        "slowEndTime": 10243
    },
    {
        "text": "A lot of us hit the \"Send\" button and ruin our careers,...",
        "startTime": 7188,
        "endTime": 10204,
        "slowStartTime": 10932,
        "slowEndTime": 15531
    },
    {
        "text": "...wishing we could take back what we've just sent.",
        "startTime": 10725,
        "endTime": 12066,
        "slowStartTime": 15787,
        "slowEndTime": 18324
    },
    {
        "text": "So here's a few rules of email that will lead to better living.",
        "startTime": 12370,
        "endTime": 16109,
        "slowStartTime": 18705,
        "slowEndTime": 24388
    },
    {
        "text": "Rule number one. Never send an email when you're mad.",
        "startTime": 16793,
        "endTime": 19591,
        "slowStartTime": 24740,
        "slowEndTime": 29612
    },
    {
        "text": "And if you want to know you're mad,...",
        "startTime": 20015,
        "endTime": 20913,
        "slowStartTime": 30173,
        "slowEndTime": 31595
    },
    {
        "text": "...just take two fingers, close your eyes, touch your eyelids.",
        "startTime": 21200,
        "endTime": 24058,
        "slowStartTime": 31627,
        "slowEndTime": 36312
    },
    {
        "text": "If they're hot, researchers say, you're mad and you should put it in the draft pile.",
        "startTime": 24550,
        "endTime": 28173,
        "slowStartTime": 36403,
        "slowEndTime": 42485
    },
    {
        "text": "Send it later.",
        "startTime": 28312,
        "endTime": 29025,
        "slowStartTime": 42618,
        "slowEndTime": 43762
    },
    {
        "text": "One of the things I've learned is that email is for saying yes.",
        "startTime": 29277,
        "endTime": 31960,
        "slowStartTime": 44065,
        "slowEndTime": 48165
    },
    {
        "text": "Email is for answering and asking questions.",
        "startTime": 32530,
        "endTime": 34690,
        "slowStartTime": 48645,
        "slowEndTime": 52260
    },
    {
        "text": "If you say no, if you criticize, if you attack, please do it in person.",
        "startTime": 35234,
        "endTime": 39297,
        "slowStartTime": 52701,
        "slowEndTime": 59170
    },
    {
        "text": "Or at the worst case, do it over the phone.",
        "startTime": 39800,
        "endTime": 41187,
        "slowStartTime": 59403,
        "slowEndTime": 62005
    },
    {
        "text": "Two more quick rules. Stamp out \"Reply to all.\"",
        "startTime": 41800,
        "endTime": 44127,
        "slowStartTime": 62094,
        "slowEndTime": 66416
    },
    {
        "text": "I call it the sortie campaign.",
        "startTime": 44523,
        "endTime": 45719,
        "slowStartTime": 66635,
        "slowEndTime": 68803
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Reply to all\"\" is considered arrogant.",
        "startTime": 46488,
        "endTime": 47970,
        "slowStartTime": 69432,
        "slowEndTime": 72085
    },
    {
        "text": "It is considered unsophisticated, especially by younger workers.",
        "startTime": 48542,
        "endTime": 51453,
        "slowStartTime": 72363,
        "slowEndTime": 77405
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't be lazy. Take the time to actually respond just to the people that need to get that email from you.",
        "startTime": 51983,
        "endTime": 57133,
        "slowStartTime": 77524,
        "slowEndTime": 85925
    },
    {
        "text": "Never send emails to your subordinates after hours, on the weekends or during holidays.",
        "startTime": 57795,
        "endTime": 63763,
        "slowStartTime": 86242,
        "slowEndTime": 95869
    },
    {
        "text": "When you send someone an email at three in the morning,...",
        "startTime": 64445,
        "endTime": 66608,
        "slowStartTime": 96517,
        "slowEndTime": 100137
    },
    {
        "text": "...you're sending the following message:...",
        "startTime": 67240,
        "endTime": 68500,
        "slowStartTime": 100710,
        "slowEndTime": 102926
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"You should feel guilty when you go home next Tuesday at 7:30 for dinner.\"",
        "startTime": 69100,
        "endTime": 73621,
        "slowStartTime": 103129,
        "slowEndTime": 110656
    },
    {
        "text": "If you have an inspiration off hours, write it, put it in the \"Send later\" pile...",
        "startTime": 74010,
        "endTime": 77802,
        "slowStartTime": 111165,
        "slowEndTime": 116928
    },
    {
        "text": "...and send it during normal business hours.",
        "startTime": 78400,
        "endTime": 80700,
        "slowStartTime": 117152,
        "slowEndTime": 121199
    }
]